Deployment
How Inngest handles Function Runs
The Inngest Platform hosts the Inngest Durable Execution Engine, responsible for triggering and maintaining the state of
**Function runs happening on your Cloud Provider**
:
The Inngest Platform relies on
[Event](\docs\events\creating-an-event-key)
and
[Signing Keys](\docs\platform\signing-keys)
, as well as
[other security mechanisms](\docs\learn\security)
, to communicate securely and reliably with the Inngest SDK.
Learn more on Inngest's Durable Execution Engine in our
["How Inngest Functions are executed" guide](\docs\learn\how-functions-are-executed)
.
